Subject: [PATCH] Cavium CN56/57XX: usb host Simple Exec files fix-up

usb related simple exec files need some fix-up when we add
usb host supoort for board cn56xx/57xx. This is a backport
from Cavium SDK 1.8.1-294

Signed-off-by: Weiwei Wang <weiwei.wang@windriver.com>
